summary:
tony, after hitting the bottle again: im sorry kid i love you
peter: i love you too and im so proud of you! youve done so well....
body:
tony, after hitting the bottle again: im sorry kid i love you

peter: i love you too and im so proud of you! youve done so well. how about you sleep it off? tomorrows a new day!

rhodey: yep, off to bed with you

tony, drunk-sobbing as rhodey tucks him in: i fucking love this kid, you know that rhodey? he is the purest being to ever exist. hes so sweet and kind and positive and i love him

summary:
Can we go back to Homecoming!Tony Stark? 
Recently betrayed, a bit battered, but looking much healthier and content than in...
body:
Can we go back to Homecoming!Tony Stark?

Recently betrayed, a bit battered, but looking much healthier and content than in Ultron and Civil War. Mentoring a spider-child and happily engaged. None of that getting run through with his own shiv, son dying in his arms and running out of oxygen in space bullshit.

Marvel, if you don’t give him a happy ending, I’ll make sure y'all don’t get one either…
